org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.behaviours

Class PercentageTokenBehaviour

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.behaviours.PercentageTokenBehaviour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Behaviour<NiTextCell>

    public class PercentageTokenBehaviour
extends java.lang.Object
implements Behaviour<NiTextCell>
    The Behaviour of a Percentageful texts column. Since the percentages are only relevant when using the column as a hierarchy, this class is identical to TextualTokenBehaviour, save for the fact that it consumes PercentageTextCell instead of TextCell. For example, just as in TextualTokenBehaviour, multiple PercentageTextCell instances are horizontally reduced to a concatenation of the alphabetically-sorted values
